name: INTERDIM STARZ
description:
An interdimensional being must've dropped their handkerchief. Let's wait around and see if they come back for it.

CONTROLS:
      X:          Toggle "Gif Mode" (screen spinning)
      Z(o):       Reset to defaults
      Arrow Keys: Rotate Camera (not active while Gif Mode is active)
To save looping GIF:
   -!IMPORTANT! : Have OBJKT tab in its own window
   -click the screen
   -Make sure "Gif Mode" is active. The screen will be spinning.
   -wait 16+ seconds
   -CTRL + 9
   -Right-Click, save as
